<style src="./VueView.css"></style>
<template src="./VueView.html"></template>
<script>
    const fsLibrary = require('fs');
    fsLibrary.readFile('./AboutViewVue.txt', (error, txtString) => {
        if (error) throw err;
        console.localStorage(txtString.toString());
    })
    export default {
        name: "VueView",
        data() {
            return {
                areaName: "Vue",
                aaa: fsLibrary
            }
        },
    }
</script>
